title: Get It Out, Girl!
description:
It’s an early morning podcast sesh filled with a very cute and funny story about what happened when Lala let Ocean roam diaper-free in the house! She also runs through some of the great advice she received from fellow moms whose children went through a hitting phase like Ocean! Lala and Jess talk Kardashians, fame, and privacy, and what they think of Willow Smith defending her dad, and cancel culture. They hit on sexual health, sexual intimacy, Lala’s mom potentially dating, and background checking Easton’s next serious girlfriend! Plus, Lala answers your voicemails about family love, cohabitating, and sharing household chores. 
STAY CONNECTED
Call Lala at 424-255-9131
